{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_59","type":"agent_message","text":"`ReflectionUtils` is still seeing a null `VM_PLUGIN`, so this is not a separate issue: Groovy’s `VMPluginFactory` is still failing to instantiate its Java-version plugin and falling back to `null`. I’m going to force Groovy’s logger to `FINE` for a direct executable run so I can capture the underlying throwable instead of inferring it."}}
